						<summary>

						<p>Slab paved in the Verandah of the post office.</p>						

						<p>It seems to register the grant of income <hi rend="italic">(vartanas)</hi> by <hi rend="italic">Vipravinōdins</hi> of Jambulamaḍaka for the merit of their twenty four families. In characters of the 16th century A.D.</p>						

